OL,3,CFire boss tribunal hears details of
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment' complaint
OL,6,FAn investigation into the conduct of
OL,7,Fthe found evidence "that may amount to
OL,8,Fbullying and harassment", according to
OL,9,Fa document seen by an employment
OL,10,Ftribunal.
OL,12,FStuart Millington was the deputy chief
OL,13,Ffire officer at North Wales Fire and
OL,14,FRescue Service before he was
OL,15,Fparachuted in to run the scandal-hit
OL,16,Ffire and rescue service in South Wales
OL,17,Fon an interim basis in February this
OL,18,Fyear.
