OL,3,CFire boss tribunal hears details of
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment' complaint
OL,6,FHowever, soon after his appointment,
OL,7,Fhe was facing an employment tribunal
OL,8,Frelated to his time in north Wales.
OL,10,FHe is accused of harassing a colleague
OL,11,Fbecause of his trade union activities.
OL,12,FThe claimant, Dafydd Roberts, says Mr
OL,13,FMillington had bullied and intimidated
OL,14,Fhim.
OL,16,FIn the tribunal hearing on Thursday, 9
OL,17,FMay, argued the case should be thrown
OL,18,Fout because Mr Roberts' claim was
OL,19,Fsubmitted outside of the permitted
OL,20,Fdeadline.
