OL,3,CFire boss tribunal hears details of
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment' complaint
OL,6,FDafydd Roberts, who joined North Wales
OL,7,FFire and Rescue Service in 2004,
OL,8,Fbrought a claim against the service
OL,9,Fafter he was allegedly bullied and
OL,10,Fharassed while working in the
OL,11,Fservice's control room in St Asaph.
OL,13,FMr Millington and Ros Thomas, the
OL,14,Fcontrol room boss, are also named as
OL,15,Frespondent in the tribunal proceedings.
