OL,3,CFire boss tribunal hears details of
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment' complaint
OL,6,FMr Roberts says he was penalised for
OL,7,Ftaking part in trade union activities
OL,8,Fand because of his disability. Papers
OL,9,Fseen by the tribunal say he is
OL,10,Fdisabled due to his anxiety and
OL,11,Fdepressive disorder.
OL,13,FThe claim made to the tribunal relates
OL,14,Fto messages sent to a Telegram group,
OL,15,Fin which Mr Roberts raised questions
OL,16,Fabout the promotion of the "relative
OL,17,Fof a senior officer".
