OL,3,CFire boss tribunal hears details of
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment' complaint
OL,6,FAccording to the documents shown to
OL,7,Fthe tribunal, the claimant's legal
OL,8,Frepresentative says Ms Thomas obtained
OL,9,Fcopies of these messages which were
OL,10,Flater shared with Mr Millington.
OL,12,FMs Thomas then allegedly questioned
OL,13,Fstaff about the messages. The tribunal
OL,14,Fpapers claim she "had obtained a copy
OL,15,Fof the Telegram messages and, in an
OL,16,Fintimidating and bullying manner,
OL,17,Fproceeded to question control room
OL,18,Foperators in attendance individually,
OL,19,Fwhile in the presence of the group,
OL,20,Fwhether they agreed with the
OL,21,Fsentiments expressed".
