OL,3,CFire boss tribunal hears details of
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment' complaint
OL,6,FThe tribunal was given a copy of the
OL,7,Freport. In it, the independent
OL,8,Finvestigation "upheld a number of the
OL,9,Ffactual allegations made by DR (Mr
OL,10,FRoberts) against SM (Mr Millington)".
OL,12,FIt continued: "The conduct complained
OL,13,Fof (if upheld) may also amount to
OL,14,Fbullying and harassment which amounts
OL,15,Fto misconduct or gross misconduct."
OL,17,FThe independent report concluded: "At
OL,18,Fa cumulative level, the investigator
OL,19,Fbelieves that there is evidence to
OL,20,Fsupport a prima facie case that may
OL,21,Famount to bullying and harassment."
