OL,6,FMr Roberts' witness statement alleges
OL,7,Fthis report was never shared with him
OL,8,Funtil the tribunal compelled the
OL,9,Fservice to provide him with a copy.
OL,11,FThe document was , in the Senedd at
OL,12,Fthe end of April. He raised questions
OL,13,Fabout whether senior Welsh Government
OL,14,Ffigures knew about the report's
OL,15,Fcontents before Mr Millington was
OL,16,Fappointed to the South Wales role by
OL,17,Ffour Welsh Government-appointed
OL,18,Fcommissioners who had been drafted in
OL,19,Fto oversee the service in the wake of
OL,20,Fa damning culture review.
