OL,6,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,7,Freject that Mr Roberts had experienced
OL,8,Fany detriment because of his trade
OL,9,Funion activities and say he was never
OL,10,Fprevented from taking part in them or
OL,11,Fdeterred from using a trade union's
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FTheir legal representative argued the
OL,15,Fcase should be called off because Mr
OL,16,FRoberts was too late in submitting his
OL,17,Fclaim to the tribunal.
