OL,3,CFire boss tribunal hears details of
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment' complaint
OL,6,FJonathan Walters, for the respondents,
OL,7,Fargued that Mr Roberts was "not
OL,8,Fsomeone who was incapable of
OL,9,Ffunctioning" during the period when he
OL,10,Fcould have brought the tribunal claim
OL,11,Fin time. He called for the case to be
OL,12,F"struck out".
OL,14,FThe tribunal's judge, Stephen Povey,
OL,15,Fadjourned the tribunal hearing to
OL,16,Fconsider the fire service's "strike
OL,17,Fout" application.
